# Dataverse Schema Design

- Every table/column/option set uses the publisher prefix
- Schema changes go through: validate → generate plan → provision
- Use `scripts/validate-schema-plan.mjs` before provisioning
- Use `scripts/generate-dataverse-plan.mjs` for execution plans
- Use `scripts/register-dataverse-data-sources.mjs` to register tables
- Option set values start at `{CHOICE_VALUE_PREFIX}0000`
- Schema mistakes are most expensive after data exists — plan first

Full details: `.github/instructions/07-dataverse-schema.instructions.md`
